[02/06/2019 03:31:19] <font color="#ffff00">del taller.</font>
[02/06/2019 03:31:21] <font color="#ffffff">- Vale.Coja un plato</font>
[02/06/2019 03:31:23] <font color="#ffffff">y lo pongalo...</font>
