[02/06/2019 12:11:44] <font color="#00ffff">recuerdo, no obstante,</font>
[02/06/2019 12:11:47] <font color="#00ffff">que aunque tomemos pollo</font>
[02/06/2019 12:11:47] <font color="#00ffff">y sea aceptable,</font>
